            <link>https://abmedia.io/ftx-investors-will-testify-against-sbf</link>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[Circle 成立研究組織 Circle Research！推出開源協議「Perimeter Protocol」]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">穩定幣發行商 Circle 於上週宣佈成立研究組織 Circle Research，致力於密碼學、ZK 技術、智能合約等領域的研究，同時也介紹推出的首個協議「Perimeter Protocol」。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">1/ 📢 Today ahead of <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/CircleForumNYC?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#CircleForumNYC</a> – we are launching a dedicated research initiative to advance open source development for the ecosystem – ‘Circle Research.’ <a href="https://t.co/54y01NtXrW">https://t.co/54y01NtXrW</a></p><p>— Circle (@circle) <a href="https://twitter.com/circle/status/1707766309952577669?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 29, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/circle-research-and-perimeter-protocol#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-651a7641c6089"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-651a7641c6089"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/circle-research-and-perimeter-protocol/#Circle_%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B_Circle_Research" title="Circle 推出研究機構 Circle Research">Circle 推出研究機構 Circle Research</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/circle-research-and-perimeter-protocol/#Circle_Research_%E9%A6%96%E5%80%8B%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E3%80%8CPerimeter_Protocol%E3%80%8D" title="Circle Research 首個協議「Perimeter Protocol」">Circle Research 首個協議「Perimeter Protocol」</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Circle_%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B_Circle_Research"></span>Circle 推出研究機構 Circle Research<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>根據 Circle <a href="https://www.circle.com/blog/circle-launches-circle-research-to-advance-open-source-development-across-crypto-blockchain-and-web3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公告</a>，Circle Research 是個致力於開源原則的研究組織，目標是為公共利益做出貢獻並加速加密貨幣、區塊鏈及 Web3 領域的創新。重點研究領域包括密碼學、加密貨幣標準、零知識證明技術及智慧合約開發。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Circle_Research_%E9%A6%96%E5%80%8B%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E3%80%8CPerimeter_Protocol%E3%80%8D"></span>Circle Research 首個協議「Perimeter Protocol」<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>伴隨著 Circle Research 的成立，其也宣佈了首個推出的協議 ── <a href="https://github.com/circlefin/perimeter-protocol" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Perimeter Protocol</a>。</p><p>Circle Research 表示 Perimeter Protocol 是一套基於開放標準建構的智能合約，旨在實現在安全、開放且無需許可的網路上進行資本的無縫交換。透過此協議，可將現實世界資產 (RWA) 和符合承保及許可標準的未抵押或低抵押貸款納入 Circle 所提供的公共協議中。</p><p>Circle 邀請開發者們對 Perimeter Protocol 的 <a href="https://github.com/circlefin/perimeter-protocol" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Github 文件</a>進行研究，並歡迎對文件提出更新建議或對其進行分岔。</p>
]]>
            </description>
