            <title>
                <![CDATA[比特幣和以太幣今晨大漲，擺脫九月魔咒，領先股市於第四季反彈？]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>邁入十月的第一個工作日，比特幣和以太幣在今晨突然大漲，資產管理公司 Lumida 執行長 Ram Ahluwalia 評論是季節性因素，這次幣價會如他所預測的，做為領先指標，先於股市反彈嗎？</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Why is Bitcoin and ETH up?</p><p>One word: Seasonality. </p><p>September is one of the worst months for Bitcoin. </p><p>Folks went long again. </p><p>Crypto, once again, has bottomed ahead of equity markets. <a href="https://t.co/IGzHiyMjqf">https://t.co/IGzHiyMjqf</a></p><p>— Ram Ahluwalia, higher for longer crypto CFA (@ramahluwalia) <a href="https://twitter.com/ramahluwalia/status/1708630460052517311?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 1, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/btc-eth-rise-this-morning-to-end-of-sep-curse#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-651a7641ca3e8"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-651a7641ca3e8"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/btc-eth-rise-this-morning-to-end-of-sep-curse/#%E6%93%BA%E8%84%AB%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E9%AD%94%E5%92%92%EF%BC%8CBTC%E3%80%81ETH_%E9%A0%98%E5%85%88%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%EF%BC%9F" title="擺脫九月魔咒，BTC、ETH 領先上漲？">擺脫九月魔咒，BTC、ETH 領先上漲？</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/btc-eth-rise-this-morning-to-end-of-sep-curse/#Ram_Ahluwalia_%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%B0%9B%E5%9C%8D%E5%B7%B2%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E8%BD%89%E8%AE%8A" title="Ram Ahluwalia 三大指標，市場氛圍已開始轉變">Ram Ahluwalia 三大指標，市場氛圍已開始轉變</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E6%93%BA%E8%84%AB%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E9%AD%94%E5%92%92%EF%BC%8CBTC%E3%80%81ETH_%E9%A0%98%E5%85%88%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%EF%BC%9F"></span>擺脫九月魔咒，BTC、ETH 領先上漲？<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>根據<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/stocks-have-had-a-great-year-cue-the-september-effect-fa922be9" target="_blank" rel="noopener">華爾街日報的報導</a>，九月傳統上是美股最疲軟的月份。自 1928 年以來，S&amp;P 500 指數在九月僅有 44.8% 的機率上漲，是唯一一個低於 50% 的月份。而九月平均跌幅為 -1.12%。</p><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-80005" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-10-02-095101.png?resize=1685%2C1105&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1685" height="1105" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-095101.png?w=1685&amp;ssl=1 1685w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-095101.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-095101.png?resize=1024%2C672&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-095101.png?resize=600%2C393&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-095101.png?resize=768%2C504&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-095101.png?resize=1536%2C1007&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p>今年九月的股市表現更是低於平均水準，S&amp;P 500 指數下跌了 4.9%，以科技股為主的 Nasdaq 指數更是下跌了 5.8%。但今晨比特幣和以太幣突然上漲，24 小時漲幅高於 3%，一個月漲幅更高達 8.21% 和 5.53%，遠勝於美股大盤指數。在正式進入第四季，幣價是否能成為先行指標，上演一波行情呢？</p><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-80010" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-10-02-100421.png?resize=1867%2C498&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1867" height="498" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-100421.png?w=1867&amp;ssl=1 1867w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-100421.png?resize=300%2C80&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-100421.png?resize=1024%2C273&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-100421.png?resize=600%2C160&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-100421.png?resize=768%2C205&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-100421.png?resize=1536%2C410&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Ram_Ahluwalia_%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%B0%9B%E5%9C%8D%E5%B7%B2%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E8%BD%89%E8%AE%8A"></span>Ram Ahluwalia 三大指標，市場氛圍已開始轉變<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>資產管理公司 Lumida 執行長 Ram Ahluwalia 在九月底時曾談到自己的戰術資產配置，他觀察的三個指標分別是：</p><ol><li>美元指數：美元已連續 10 週走強，他預期在美元熱潮結束之前風險偏好不會恢復。</li><li>半導體 (SMH)：代表著 AI 敍事的 SMH 指數目前仍未走強，不過他預期將在第四季恢復。</li><li>美國十年期公債：目前的敍事為「更高更久」。幾個月前，市場預計 2024 年將降息約 6 次，但現在已降為 2 次。而市場有沒有可能轉變為零降息的預期呢？</li></ol><p>而其最新的推文指出，根據高盛的報告顯示，避險基金在七週來首次購買科技股，也回補了半導體的空頭部位並出售了能源股。美元已經連續 11 週上漲，而且已經過度擴張。市場氛圍開始轉變！</p><p>幣價是否會如他所預測的，做為領先指標，先於股市反彈，並如歷史般在第四季繳出亮眼的成績呢？</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Goldman’s Prime Report shows HFs bought Tech stocks for the first time in 7 weeks. </p><p>HFs also covered shorts in semis and sold energy. </p><p>The USD has run 11 weeks straight up and is over-extended. </p><p>The vibe is starting to shift. <a href="https://t.co/1jrHiF9Cb6">https://t.co/1jrHiF9Cb6</a><a href="https://t.co/xfTsEnfi0Q">pic.twitter.com/xfTsEnfi0Q</a></p><p>— Ram Ahluwalia, higher for longer crypto CFA (@ramahluwalia) <a href="https://twitter.com/ramahluwalia/status/1708623810696486936?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 1, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
]]>
