        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[比特幣現貨 ETF 全軍覆沒！Invesco Galaxy 仍提交以太坊現貨 ETF 申請]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>雖然美國聯邦政府關門警報暫時解除，但美國證券交易委員會 (SEC) 已公告全面推遲比特幣現貨 ETF 的決定。目前提出申請的八檔比特幣現貨 ETF ，包括富達 (Fidelity)、VanEck 和 WisdomTree 也將延後至明年一月中做為下次審核時間。而另一邊，各大資產管理機構仍爭相申請以太坊現貨 ETF，目前已有四檔以太坊現貨 ETF 等待批准。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/all-btc-spot-etf-delayed-but-amc-still-file-for-eth-spot-etf#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-651a7641cea54"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-651a7641cea54"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/all-btc-spot-etf-delayed-but-amc-still-file-for-eth-spot-etf/#SEC_%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8_ETF_%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91" title="SEC 對比特幣現貨 ETF 的質疑">SEC 對比特幣現貨 ETF 的質疑</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/all-btc-spot-etf-delayed-but-amc-still-file-for-eth-spot-etf/#%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%9D%8A%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8_ETF_%E6%AD%A3%E5%89%8D%E4%BB%86%E5%BE%8C%E7%B9%BC%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B" title="以太坊現貨 ETF 正前僕後繼地申請">以太坊現貨 ETF 正前僕後繼地申請</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="SEC_%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8_ETF_%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91"></span>SEC 對比特幣現貨 ETF 的質疑<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>在&nbsp;<a href="https://www.sec.gov/files/rules/sro/cboebzx/2023/34-98614.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SEC 公告的文件</a>中，希望評論者能提出以下意見</p><ul><li>對於交易所的提議是否能防止詐欺和操縱行為和做法？</li><li>對比特幣市場的流動性和透明度以及比特幣市場對操縱的敏感性的普遍看法？</li><li>與加密貨幣交易所 Coinbase 達成的監視共享協議是否有助於「偵測、調查和阻止詐欺和操縱」？</li></ul><p>評論員有 21 天的時間提交書面資料、觀點和論據，然後還有 35 天的反駁期限，這意味著批准過程將至少再拖延幾個月。</p><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-79997" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-10-02-072928.png?resize=1292%2C628&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1292" height="628" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-072928.png?w=1292&amp;ssl=1 1292w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-072928.png?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-072928.png?resize=1024%2C498&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-072928.png?resize=600%2C292&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-02-072928.png?resize=768%2C373&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%9D%8A%E7%8F%BE%E8%B2%A8_ETF_%E6%AD%A3%E5%89%8D%E4%BB%86%E5%BE%8C%E7%B9%BC%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B"></span>以太坊現貨 ETF 正前僕後繼地申請<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>雖然比特幣現貨 ETF 的申請仍未開花結果，但各大資產管理機構仍趁勢提出以太坊現貨 ETF 的申請，根據彭博分析師 James Seyffart 的推文，目前已有 Ark 與 21Shares 合作推出的以太坊 ETF<a href="https://abmedia.io/ark-invest-files-for-spot-ether-etf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> (ARKE)</a>、景順 (Invesco) 與 Galaxy 合作推出的 Invesco Galaxy Ethereum ETF、VanEck Ethereum ETF 以及 Hashdex Nasdaq Ethereum ETF 四檔以太坊現貨 ETF 等待批准。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">We have a 4th Spot <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Ethereum?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Ethereum</a> ETF Filing. Invesco/Galaxy joins VanEck, Ark/21Shares, &amp; Hashdex. <a href="https://t.co/WzakKsmyjO">https://t.co/WzakKsmyjO</a></p><p>— James Seyffart (@JSeyff) <a href="https://twitter.com/JSeyff/status/1707776396607590458?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 29, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
]]>
            </description>
