            <title>
                <![CDATA[下週一將有九檔以太坊期貨 ETF 上線？規模將達七億美元]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>似乎是為了避免美國政府關門的危機，這幾天美國證券交易委員會 (SEC) 快馬加鞭為近期的 ETF 做出批准或是<a href="https://abmedia.io/sec-delay-valkyrie-bitwise-blackblock-invesco-btc-spot-etf-again" target="_blank" rel="noopener">延後</a>的公告。根據彭博 ETF 分析師 James Seyffart 的統計，下週一預計有九檔以太坊期貨 ETF 上線。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/there-may-be-9-eth-future-etfs-go-live-next-monday#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-651a7641d7ec7"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-651a7641d7ec7"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/there-may-be-9-eth-future-etfs-go-live-next-monday/#%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%B1%E4%B8%80%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E6%9C%89%E4%B9%9D%E6%AA%94%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%9D%8A%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8_ETF_%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A" title="下週一預計有九檔以太坊期貨 ETF 上線">下週一預計有九檔以太坊期貨 ETF 上線</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/there-may-be-9-eth-future-etfs-go-live-next-monday/#Valkyrie_%E5%81%B7%E8%B7%91%EF%BC%9F%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%89%E8%AE%8A%E6%95%B8%EF%BC%9F" title="Valkyrie 偷跑？還是有變數？">Valkyrie 偷跑？還是有變數？</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%B1%E4%B8%80%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E6%9C%89%E4%B9%9D%E6%AA%94%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%9D%8A%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8_ETF_%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A"></span>下週一預計有九檔以太坊期貨 ETF 上線<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>繼資產管理公司 Valkyrie 宣佈其比特幣期貨 ETF 轉型為混合比特幣和以太坊期貨 ETF ( 商品代碼仍維持 BTF) 獲準後，多家基金公司也磨拳擦掌，根據彭博 ETF 分析師 James Seyffart 的統計，下週一預計有九檔以太坊期貨 ETF 上線。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">OKAY:  This looks to be the full list of <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Ethereum?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Ethereum</a>  Futures ETFs that will be given SEC accelerated approval to launch on Monday. Assuming they are all operationally ready to go &amp; assuming no last minute entrants. A potential 9 ETFs with ETH futures trading on Monday <a href="https://t.co/eQF6MWL4kP">pic.twitter.com/eQF6MWL4kP</a></p><p>— James Seyffart (@JSeyff) <a href="https://twitter.com/JSeyff/status/1707866932311957577?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 29, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><p>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/valkyrie-eth-future-etf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SEC 批准首檔「混合型」以太坊期貨 ETF！Valkyrie 拔得頭籌，10/3 開始交易</a>)</p><p>這也將掀起一波 ETF 的價格戰，ProShares 目前準備推出的三檔以太坊 ETF 費用率為 0.95%，而 Bitwise 的兩檔 ETF 的費用率為 0.85 %，VanEck 則為 0.66 % 。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Valkyrie_%E5%81%B7%E8%B7%91%EF%BC%9F%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%89%E8%AE%8A%E6%95%B8%EF%BC%9F"></span>Valkyrie 偷跑？還是有變數？<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>不過，最先宣佈獲準的 Valkyrie 卻在隨後發布了 497 消息，表明在他們正式上線前不會購買以太坊期貨，並將平倉之前購買的以太坊期貨。也為這些以太坊期貨 ETF 是否能如預期般上市增添了變數！</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">The plot thickens, Valkyrie just put out 497 that they are in fact not going to buy Ether futures until they are live (prob Tue) and are going to sell the Eth futures they bought (in an effort to jump line a bit). SEC must have threatened them to cut it out. Damn. <a href="https://t.co/yDkggCw3d1">https://t.co/yDkggCw3d1</a><a href="https://t.co/cKaV7k7AJs">pic.twitter.com/cKaV7k7AJs</a></p><p>— Eric Balchunas (@EricBalchunas) <a href="https://twitter.com/EricBalchunas/status/1707752633887306046?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 29, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><p>Valkyrie 的 BTF 原本是交易比特幣期貨的 ETF，此次是用轉型的方式提出申請，由常理推斷，在覈準日之前本不應該先行購買以太坊期貨，筆者認為，將偷跑的以太坊期貨平倉，應該也是為了合規，待正式上線後再開始執行新策略也不遲！</p><p>而市場期待的藉由 ETF 的推出，為投資者帶來新的投資管道，進而增加流動性和降低費用率，此前預估，以太坊期貨 ETF 的規模將來到 7 億美元。</p><p>(<a href="https://abmedia.io/eth-future-etf-may-be-approved-by-sec-in-oct" target="_blank" rel="noopener">彭博：以太坊期貨 ETF 有望 10 月批准！會對市場帶來哪些影響？</a>)</p>
